additional_info:
4/9/2015 Update: Theme now applies to the whole site! I also fixed some issues with new UI, and changed the background to something that requires less personal resizing. The old images are still available just swap out both body tags, and resize as necessary, for:

Body{background-image: url(http://i.imgur.com/LMPfmTU.png), url(http://i.imgur.com/IMPKwW8.png); background-repeat: no-repeat;  background-position: left center, right center; background-size: 210px 760px, 210px 800px; background-color: black; background-attachment: fixed; }


2/18/2015 Update: Theme now applies to chat! Also a few minor improvements including attack UI box.

